These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, basketball, biathlon, cricket
4 different games are played: monopoly, domino, poker, chess
1. the person playing chess is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person playing domino##1
3. the person who's sport is cricket is in an odd position##4
4. the person playing poker is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3
5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Sport   | skateboarding | basketball | cricket | biathlon |
| Game        | monopoly | domino   | chess | poker    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
City: berlin, venice, marseilles, colone
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, game, cain, siglo
1. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
2. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
3. the cain-smoker is in an odd position##4
4. the fonseca-smoker is the person traveling to berlin##1
5. the game-smoker is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
6. the fonseca-smoker is the person traveling to berlin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| City   | marseilles | berlin  | venice  | colone |
| Cigar   | siglo    | fonseca | cain | game    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, country, metal, salsa
4 different games are played: whist, backgammon, snooker, mah-jongg
1. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg##3
2. the fan of metal is in an even position##4
3. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the fan of country##3
4. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
5. the person playing whist is in an odd position##4
6. the fan of country is on the right of the fan of metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Music-Genre          | salsa | metal | country    | funk      |
| Game   | snooker        | mah-jongg     | whist | backgammon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, iced-tea, soy-milk, coffee
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, malaysian, russian, turkish
1. the person drinking iced-tea is between the polish and the turkish##2
2. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
3. the russian is in an odd position##4
4. the malaysian is on the left of the turkish##1
5. the malaysian is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Beverage         | coffee | mirinda | iced-tea | soy-milk |
| Nationality   | russian       | polish   | malaysian    | turkish  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, dannemann, blend, prince
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, balloon-flower, sunflower, bellflower
1. the blend-smoker is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
2. the person who growsballoon-flower is the prince-smoker##1
3. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
4. the dannemann-smoker is on the far left##1
5. the blend-smoker is in an odd position##4
6. the person who growszinnia is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Cigar   | dannemann  | aristoff    | blend   | prince       |
| Flower   | zinnia | bellflower | sunflower | balloon-flower |

