.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-6::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, trike, subway, airplane
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, pink, apricot, coral
1. the person who likes pink is in an even position##4
2. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
3. the person driving the subway is in an odd position##4
4. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
5. the person who likes apricot is on the left or right of the person who likes blue##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Transport   | subway      | trike | airplane | ship |
| Color   | coral | pink     | blue  | apricot  |

