.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, baseball, rowing, water-polo
House: tower, colonial, gothic-revival, cape-cod
1. the cape-cod house is in an odd position##4
2. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the tower house##1
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
4. the cape-cod house is the person who's sport is rugby##1
5. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left or right of the tower house##3
6. the colonial house is on the right of the tower house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Sport   | rugby | water-polo | rowing | baseball    |
| House     | cape-cod | gothic-revival  | tower     | colonial |

