.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, bellflower, iris, begonia
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, radish, blueberry, grapes
1. the person eating grapes is on the left or right of the person who growsbellflower##3
2. the person who growsbegonia is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating grapes is on the left or right of the person who growsbegonia##3
4. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
5. the person who growsazalea is between the person who growsbegonia and the person who growsbellflower##2
6. the person eating radish is in an odd position##4
7. the person eating radish is between the person who growsazalea and the person eating blueberry##2
8. the person who growsazalea is on the left or right of the person who growsbellflower##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Flower   | bellflower | azalea      | begonia | iris |
| Food   | asparagus  | grapes | radish    | blueberry            |

