.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, quad-bike, ship, tram
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, snowboarding, surfing, baseball
1. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
2. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
3. the person who's sport is soccer is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the person driving the ship##2
4. the person who's sport is soccer is in an odd position##4
5. the person driving the ship is the person who's sport is surfing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Transport   | tram | quad-bike   | scooter | ship |
| Sport    | baseball     | snowboarding | soccer     | surfing  |

