.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, iris, dahlia, balloon-flower
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, skydiving, traveling, chess
1. the person who growsbellflower is the person who's hobby is chess##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
3. the person who's hobby is chess is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person who growsdahlia##2
4. the person who growsbellflower is in an odd position##4
5. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
6. the person who growsiris is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Flower      | iris       | dahlia   | bellflower | balloon-flower |
| Hobby   | traveling | skydiving | chess        | hiking    |

