2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the australian##1
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
4. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the mexican##1
5. the french is on the left or right of the mexican##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Nationality   | australian   | polish   | french      | mexican      |
| Hobby      | dancing | magic-tricks | cooking | board-games |

