.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, quad-bike, roller, boat
House: colonial, palace, tower, victorian
1. the person driving the ship is between the colonial house and the person driving the quad-bike##2
2. the person driving the roller is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the victorian house##1
4. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
5. the victorian house is in an odd position##4
6. the tower house is on the left of the palace house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Transport   | boat | quad-bike         | ship   | roller |
| House   | tower    | palace | victorian | colonial   |

