.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-16::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: aconite, marigold, bellflower, poppy
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, april, november, october
1. the person who's birthday is in october is the person who growsbellflower##1
2. the person who's birthday is in november is the person who growsaconite##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is the person who growspoppy##1
4. the person who growsbellflower is on the left or right of the person who growspoppy##3
5. the person who growsaconite is in an even position##4
6. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Flower   | marigold | aconite | bellflower    | poppy |
| Birthday   | may   | november  | october | april     |

