.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
City: hamburg, rome, marseilles, edinburgh
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, june, may, november
1. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
2. the person traveling to marseilles is in an even position##4
3. the person who's birthday is in june is the person traveling to marseilles##1
4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3
5. the person who's birthday is in june is between the person who's birthday is in november and the person who's birthday is in may##2
6. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| City         | edinburgh   | marseilles | hamburg | rome    |
| Birthday   | may | june  | november     | january |

