.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: pink, red, white, green
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, satire, sports, western
1. the person watching satire movies is on the far left##1
2. the person who likes white is on the left or right of the person who likes pink##3
3. the person who likes green is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
5. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
6. the person watching sports movies is in an even position##4
7. the person watching time-travel movies is the person who likes red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Color   | green | pink    | white       | red |
| Movie-Genre       | satire  | sports | western | time-travel  |

