.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, juice, cola, almond-milk
House: victorian, farmhouse, cottage, modern
1. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the cottage house is on the left or right of the victorian house##3
3. the victorian house is on the left of the cottage house##1
4. the farmhouse house is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
5. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the cottage house##1
6. the victorian house is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | juice | cola | fanta  | almond-milk |
| House     | victorian      | cottage       | farmhouse | modern     |

