.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, punk, folk, hip-hop
There are 4 different nationalities: american, polish, french, mexican
1. the fan of punk is in an even position##4
2. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the american##3
3. the polish is between the fan of salsa and the american##2
4. the fan of punk is on the far left or far right##3
5. the french is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
6. the french is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Music-Genre         | salsa | folk   | hip-hop | punk |
| Nationality   | mexican          | polish | american         | french  |

 